channel.title: Need help! I can't remove some program from my computer!
channel.description:
Omg.. this looks really serious!! :( I downloaded "pimpscape.rar" the source.., and i decide.. i don't want that source anymore, so, on the desktop, i right-click the pimpscape and "delete" some error pop-up, error said: [code] Cannot delete .hadees...: Cannot find the specified file.
Make sure you specify the correct path and file name. [/code]
WTF??? Please help!!!! And when I want to remove "Command Maker V3", some error pop-up: [code] Cannot delete Command Maker V3.jar: Its is being used by other person or program.
Close any programs that might using the file and try again.[/code] HUH?? All of the program is closed, well.. same error! :( :( :(
:confused: :confused: Please help! :confused: :confused:
